<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Check Your Prescription Schedule Attachment</title>
</head>

<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f0f4f8;">
  <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%"
    style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
    <tr>
      <td
        style="padding: 40px 30px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6a11cb 0%, #2575fc 100%); text-align: center;">
        <h1 style="color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold;">Your Prescription Schedule</h1>
        <p style="color: #ffffff; margin: 10px 0 0; font-size: 18px;">Please Click on the Attachment Below!</p>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 40px 30px;">
        <p style="font-size: 18px; color: #333333; margin-bottom: 30px; text-align: center;">Hello, <%= name %>
        </p>
        <p style="font-size: 18px; color: #333333; margin-bottom: 30px; text-align: center;">We've attached your
          personalized prescription schedule to this email. <strong>Please click on the attachment</strong> to view your
          timetable.</p>
        <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin-bottom: 30px;">
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 30px; background-color: #e8f0fe; border-radius: 15px; text-align: center;">
              <h2 style="color: #2575fc; margin: 0 0 15px; font-size: 26px;">⚠ Click the Attachment <b>ONLY</b></h2>
              <p style="color: #333333; margin: 0; font-size: 18px;">Your prescription schedule is attached to this
                email. <strong>Click to open and view your schedule.</strong></p>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td
        style="padding: 20px; background-color: #f8f9fa; text-align: center; border-bottom-left-radius: 20px; border-bottom-right-radius: 20px;">
        <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #999999; margin: 0;">© 2025 Helix. All rights reserved.</p>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>

</html>